@node Main "PenDenTive - Documentation"

                            'PenDenTive' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'PenDenTive' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on an 8 by 10 tiles board
in which you try to make alignments of tiles of the same type, either
horizontally or vertically, the more aligments of 3 or more tiles you
make in one move, the more points you get.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
               @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
               @{"          History          " link histo}
               @{"        Legal stuff        " link legal}
               @{"          Credits          " link credits}

